lines.text: It's snakes. I can't stand snakes!

[laughs]
A big strong man like you and you're afraid of little old snakes?
My stomach. It hurts. Must be... the idea of snakes all the time!
Thank you for killing those other two bastards. My name's Larry. And I believe that you're looking for me.
Why did you order your men to rape Rose? She'd never done you any harm, you turd.
She isn't under yet. Give her more gas.

[after sucking on Rose's poisoned flesh]
The wine! There must have been something in it!
Not the wine. My nipples, you jerk.
What's the use of those photos you sent me? It's only Morris and his three assholes.
